msgid "Priority 3: Outages greater than 72 hours impacting business continuity"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/process/security.md:420
msgid "Outage of online CRM system"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/process/security.md:423
msgid "Reduced ability to continue sales operations"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/process/security.md:426
msgid ""
"While there is no current failover plan should our online CRM system "
"become disrupted, we have SLAs with our CRM vendor--which is used by "
"thousands of other organizations--and believe the probability of "
"sustained outage is low."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/process/security.md:428
msgid "Priority 4: Outages greater than 10 days impacting business continuity"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/process/security.md:430
msgid "Outage of online HR and intranet systems"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/process/security.md:433
msgid "Reduced ability to continue HR and internal operations"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/process/security.md:436
msgid ""
"While there is no current failover plan should our online HR or intranet "
"system become disrupted, we have SLAs with our  vendors--which is used by"
